genresAdvancedInfo.name: salsa urbana
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Salsa urbana is a modern take on the traditional salsa music, blending urban beats and electronic sounds with the classic salsa rhythm. It's characterized by its energetic and upbeat tempo, and often features rap verses and reggaeton influences.
